：有個人被強姦，你唔好問我邊個、幾時、邊間房，咁你都證明唔到真定假，其實又無意思。對醫護來講，最需要保護的係病人。可能佢想精神上身體上休息吓，等自己ready先公開，甚至決定以後都唔公開，我哋都應尊重，因為最大嘅受害者係佢，我哋無權去代佢決定。當然，如果有當事人決定公開，我哋一定會為佢作證啦。」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞, 醫生專訪<br />\n講到咁即係有, 無既話邊會曬咁多口水<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258C%25A1%2F&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c7883312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258C%25A1%2F&h=8db76ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"a6c11537f48968c6c49657b71e531fbd3205f2e8","tid":1563753,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e619e2f5eee2fcb0fe170a45504f6b2c71cda0","tid":1563753,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a